{"tid":1674210,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【10.26長龍召喚】香港人，開飯！集合地點：自區最黃嘅店","createTime":"2019-10-25T05:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T06:04:11.000Z","uid":280192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d975ccd28e508c14bdaaacde58bfebff31858184","tid":1674210,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:41:58.000Z","msg":"10.26明日可集合在自區最黃的鋪，如果無乜勁黃鋪，就去隔離區，再唔係就去最近嘅龍門冰室。<br />\n<br />\n有人話應分散懲罰小店，有人話集中排金店造勢。其實各人喜歡，很難相逼，相輔相成。最理想係懲罰完小店，唔打算食都去金店排隊召喚長龍。<br />\n<br />\n食飯就係示威，示威就係食飯。<br />\n<br />\n記住食未必係重點，店外200黑衣人排隊，可以試下排到2000人。今次係和理非活動，留返條通道，沿途保持禮貌，盡量減少衝突，上千人效果已經好大，附近藍店要收皮。"},{"pid":"888f7ca3a6a14ff4475be4980b60dec6404bb4d1","tid":1674210,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:43:01.000Z","msg":"抗爭示威生活化！"},{"pid":"3657bde0b1edf09a62624571cc85117d7e1c75b8","tid":1674210,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:45:08.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"1363f83bbc7a245fc8ded24cbccd66db1d2de594","tid":1674210,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"記得醫護集會都係星期六 <br />\n同時做"},{"pid":"572788c3f63ffa8e3b8b5caeeb017a2926a1613e","tid":1674210,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"提大家今個星期六日有咩活動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期六 10 &middot; 26 醫護抗暴 - 醫療專職集會</strong></span><br />\n- 18:00 遮打花園 [已獲不反對通知書]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期日 10 &middot; 27 <br />\n追究警暴 守護民眾記者 守護穆斯林</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 尖沙咀梳士巴利道公園<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期日 10 &middot; 27 自由之鶴追悼會</strong></span><br />\n- 16:00 - 20:00 觀塘海濱公園"},{"pid":"8b84b05d3ce818bb2781dfe73a3e517adae5558d","tid":1674210,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:04:11.000Z","msg":"25/10(Fri)： 12點半九龍公園光復學界人鏈，7點HKDI將軍澳人鏈<br />\n26/10(Sat)： 12點18區Suck-神獸[長龍]，2點半遮打玫瑰經祈禱會，6點遮打醫療專職集會<br />\n27/10(Sun)： 3點尖沙咀守護清真寺，4點觀塘自由紙鶴追悼會<br />\n<br />\n香港人抗爭日程表<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=e3d60cb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a>"}]}